name: Quote number should display as custom quote number for  LOB

testSteps.description: 1: Quote number should display as custom quote number for  LOB ({Company=Protective Insurance Company, QuoteNumber=Quote 01--000006506-0})

children.description:
Given underwriter does select <LOB> from the New Business create quote tile as
| Workers Compensation |
When underwriter fills Quote screen form
And selects the underwriting company Protective Insurance Company
Then the Quote number Quote 01--000006506-0 should be generated and should be visible on top left corner at all times
